cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.LG 

This paper is primarily focused on image synthesis and style transfer, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) categories. The use of deep learning techniques and neural networks also suggests that it could be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the mention of video stylization suggests that it could also be categorized under multimedia (cs.MM).
